<!-- About Start -->
<div class="container-xxl py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s" style="min-height: 400px;">
                <div class="position-relative h-100">
                    <img class="img-fluid position-absolute w-100 h-100" src="~/img/about.jpg" alt="" style="object-fit: cover;">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                <h6 class="section-title bg-white text-start text-primary pe-3">About Us</h6>
                <h1 class="mb-4">Welcome to eLEARNING</h1>

                <h5 class="mb-4">
                    Transforming aspirations into achievements, we pave the way to excellence with free courses, igniting the journey to success for every student
                </h5>
                <h6 class="mb-4">
                    No fluff, just the good stuff!
                </h6>
                <p class="mb-4">We don't want to waste your time with boring stuff you don't need. So I've made sure my courses are clear, concise, to the point, and free of technical jargon. No rambling or repetition, just the essentials you need to succeed, explained in plain English</p>
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <p>We are a non-profit e-learning platform committed to democratizing education in the field of computer science. Our mission is to aggregate and present freely available resources from platforms like YouTube in a curated and organized manner, making them easily accessible to aspiring computer scientists worldwide.</p>

                    <p>We recognize the abundance of valuable educational content scattered across various platforms online. Our purpose is to streamline the process of discovering these resources by curating them into categorized lists and providing additional context and guidance to help learners navigate their options effectively.</p>

                    <p>Our platform is built on the principle of making education accessible to all, without any financial barriers. We do not host any content ourselves; instead, we meticulously curate links to free courses and tutorials available on reputable platforms such as YouTube, ensuring learners have access to quality resources at no cost.</p>

                    <p>We understand that starting a journey in computer science can be daunting, especially with the vast amount of content available online. Our platform aims to empower newcomers by offering a curated selection of free courses, tutorials, and educational resources, making it easier for them to embark on their learning journey with confidence.</p>

                    <p>Learning is not just about accessing content; it's also about connecting with others who share similar interests and challenges. We foster a supportive community where learners can engage with each other, share insights, and collaborate on projects, creating a network of mutual support and encouragement.</p>

                    <p>Meet the dedicated individuals who work tirelessly to curate and organize the vast array of educational resources available online. Our team consists of passionate volunteers with diverse backgrounds in computer science, education, and technology, united by a common goal of making learning accessible to all.</p>

                    <p>Interested in contributing to our mission of democratizing education? There are several ways you can get involved. Whether it's suggesting new resources, helping with content curation, or spreading the word about our platform, your support is invaluable in helping us reach more learners around the world.</p>

                    <p>Have questions, suggestions, or feedback? We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to us via email or through our contact form, and we'll be happy to assist you in any way we can.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

            
        
    </div>
</div>
<!-- About End -->